import React from 'react'
import {
    SidebarContainer,
    Icon,
    CloseIcon,
} from "./SidebarElements"

const Sidebar = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <SidebarContainer>
                <Icon>
                    <CloseIcon />
                </Icon>
                <SidebarWrapper>
                    <SidebarMenu>
                        <SidebarLink to="about">
                            About Me
                        </SidebarLink>
                        <SidebarLink to="about">
                            CS Projects
                        </SidebarLink>
                        <SidebarLink to="about">
                            Extracurriculars
                        </SidebarLink>
                        <SidebarLink to="about">
                            Contact Me
                        </SidebarLink>
                    </SidebarMenu>
                </SidebarWrapper>
            </SidebarContainer>
        </>
    )
}

export default Sidebar
